Package: Dense2SparseHDF5
Type: Package
Title: Memory efficient convert a dens HDF5 matrix to a sparse matrix
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-02-07
Author: Stefan Lang
Maintainer: Stefan Lang <Stefan.Lang@med.lu.se>
Description: Loom files may contain huge dense matrices. To load them into R is ofen not possible.
        To reduce this problem this package reads the martix in chunks populates the sparse matrix chunk by chunk implemented cin c++.
